---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Irrlichter | Info"
  description="Background, method, and participation paths for the Irrlichter bog art and environment project."
  lang="en"
  currentPath="/en/info"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Info</h1>
    <p>
      Irrlichter combines artistic practice, environmental education, and local field
      observation. The bog is treated as a living archive where ecological and cultural
      layers become visible over time.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Project approach and method</h2>
    <p>
      The archive grows through small iterations. Each publication is a timestamped
      snapshot and part of an ongoing logbook with contextual notes and media-specific
      perspectives.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Bog context</h2>
    <p>
      Bogs store carbon, regulate water systems, and offer refuge to sensitive species.
      Irrlichter makes these relationships tangible through both sensory and documentary
      formats.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>Contribute</h2>
    <p>
      Local knowledge, notes from the field, and collaborations are welcome. A dedicated
      contact section will be added in the next iteration.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
